The implementation satisfies the task scope. "'`LiveBuffer` exposes `source_name`, `capture_path`, `freshness`, `rms`, `spectral_profile`, and `transform_history` directly via dataclass fields and supports state updates through `refresh()`.

`SampleBankArchive` persists selected clips into source-specific archive subdirectories, writes a companion JSON metadata file, and returns `None` when the source file is missing.

